ason|2017]] || [[2017 Carolina Panthers season|CAR]] \n| '''16''' || '''16''' || 291 || 492 || 59.1 || 3,302 || 6.7 || 22 || 16 || 80.7 || '''139''' || '''754''' || 5.4 || 69 || 6 || 9 || 1\n|-\n! [[2018 NFL season|2018]] || [[2018 Carolina Panthers season|CAR]] \n| 14 || 14 || '''320''' || 471 || '''67.5''' || 3,395 || 7.2 || 24 || 13 || 94.2 || 101 || 488 || 4.8 || 29 || 4 || 6 || 0\n|-\n! [[2019 NFL season|2019]] || [[2019 Carolina Panthers season|CAR]] \n| 2 || 2 || 50 || 89 || 56.2 || 572 || 6.4 || 0 || 1 || 71.0 || 5 || \u22122 || \u22120.4 || 3 || 0 || 2 || 2\n|- class=\"sortbottom\" style=\"background:#eee;\"\n! colspan=\"2\"| Totals\n! 125 || 124 || 2,371 || 3,980 || 59.6 || 29,041 || 7.3 || 182 || 108 || 86.1 || 934 || 4,806 || 5.1 || 72T || 58 || 52 || 20\n|}\n\n===Postseason===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Team\n! colspan=\"2\"| Games\n! colspan=\"8\"| Passing\n! colspan=\"5\"| Rushing\n! colspan=\"2\"| Fumbles\n|-\n! GP !! GS !! {{Tooltip| Cmp | Completed passes}} !! {{Tooltip|Att|Pass attempts}} !! {{Tooltip|Pct|Completion percentage}} !! {{Tooltip|Yds|Passing yards}} !! {{Tooltip|Avg|Yards per pass attempt}} !! {{Tooltip|TD|Passing touchdowns}} !! {{Tooltip|INT|Interceptions thrown}} !! {{Tooltip| Rate | Passer rating}} !! {{Tooltip|Att|Rushing attempts}} !! {{Tooltip|Yds|Rushing yards}} !! {{Tooltip|Avg|Average yards per rush}} !! {{Tooltip|Lng|Longest rush}} !! {{Tooltip|TD|Rushing touchdowns}} !! {{Tooltip|Fum|Fumbles}} !! {{Tooltip|Lost|Fumbles lost}}\n|-\n! [[2013\u201314 NFL playoffs|2013]] || [[2013 Carolina Panthers season|CAR]] \n| 1 || 1 || 16 || 25 || '''64.0''' || 267 || '''10.7''' || 1 || 2 || 79.9 || 10 || 54 || '''5.4''' || 11 || 0 || 0 || 0\n|-\n! [[2014\u201315 NFL playoffs|2014]] || [[2014 Carolina Panthers season|CAR]] \n| 2 || 2 || 41 || 68 || 60.3 || 444 || 6.5 || '''4''' || '''3''' || 80.8 || 18 || 72 || 4.0 || 13 || 0 || '''3''' || '''2'''\n|-\n! style=